    PlayerSpawnPhantomsEvent.setResult(@NotNull Result result)
    The result of this event controls if phantoms will be spawned.
    If the result is ALLOW, phantoms will always be spawned; If the result is DENY, phantoms will never be spawned; If the result is DEFAULT, vanilla checks will be run to determine if the spawn may occur.
